                product_id = $4, variant_id = $5, quantity_returned = $6,
                condition = $7, action = $8, unit_cost = $9, line_total = $10,
                notes = $11, updated_by = $12, updated_at = $13
            WHERE tenant_id = $1 AND rma_item_id = $2 AND rma_id = $3 AND deleted_at IS NULL
